## Detailed Test Matrix

### AWS Resources

| # | Test | Command (from VPS) | Expected Result |
|---|------|-------------------|-----------------|
| 1 | S3 bucket exists | `aws s3api head-bucket --bucket gblockparty-builds` | No error |
| 2 | S3 write | `echo test \| aws s3 cp - s3://gblockparty-builds/_verify/test.txt` | Success |
| 3 | S3 read | `aws s3 cp s3://gblockparty-builds/_verify/test.txt -` | Outputs "test" |
| 4 | S3 delete | `aws s3 rm s3://gblockparty-builds/_verify/test.txt` | Success |
| 5 | S3 public access blocked | `curl -s https://gblockparty-builds.s3.amazonaws.com/` from external | Access Denied |
| 6 | Secrets Manager read | `aws secretsmanager describe-secret --secret-id gblockparty/jwt-secret` | Returns JSON |
| 7 | Secrets Manager list | `aws secretsmanager list-secrets --filters Key=name,Values=gblockparty/` | Returns 5 secrets |
| 8 | RDS connect (SSL) | `psql "$DATABASE_URL" -c "SELECT 1"` | Returns 1 |
| 9 | RDS SSL enforced | `psql "$DATABASE_URL" -c "SHOW ssl"` | Returns "on" |

### VPS

| # | Test | Command | Expected Result |
|---|------|---------|-----------------|
| 10 | Docker version | `docker --version` | 24+ or 27+ |
| 11 | Docker Compose version | `docker compose version` | v2.x |
| 12 | Docker hello-world | `docker run --rm hello-world` | Success |
| 13 | Docker network | `docker network inspect gblockparty` | JSON output |
| 14 | UFW status | `sudo ufw status verbose` | Active, deny incoming |
| 15 | Disk usage | `df -h /` | Under 50% |
| 16 | Memory | `free -m` | 6000+ MB available |

### Caddy

| # | Test | Command | Expected Result |
|---|------|---------|-----------------|
| 17 | Caddy running | `systemctl is-active caddy` | active |
| 18 | Caddy enabled | `systemctl is-enabled caddy` | enabled |
| 19 | Caddyfile valid | `caddy validate --config /etc/caddy/Caddyfile` | Valid |
| 20 | Admin API | `curl -s http://localhost:2019/config/` | JSON response |
| 21 | HTTP response | `curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code}" http://localhost:80` | 200 or 308 |

### DNS & TLS

| # | Test | Command (from any machine) | Expected Result |
|---|------|---------------------------|-----------------|
| 22 | Root DNS | `dig +short A yourdomain.dev` | Cloudflare IPs |
| 23 | Wildcard DNS | `dig +short A test.yourdomain.dev` | Cloudflare IPs |
| 24 | Platform DNS | `dig +short A platform.yourdomain.dev` | Cloudflare IPs |
| 25 | Preview DNS | `dig +short A pr-42--myapp.yourdomain.dev` | Cloudflare IPs |
| 26 | HTTPS TLS | `curl -v https://platform.yourdomain.dev 2>&1 \| grep SSL` | TLS handshake OK |
| 27 | CF headers | `curl -sI https://platform.yourdomain.dev \| grep cf-ray` | cf-ray present |

### Security

| # | Test | Command (from external) | Expected Result |
|---|------|------------------------|-----------------|
| 28 | Port 22 closed | `nc -zv <VPS_IP> 22` | Refused/timeout |
| 29 | Port 2019 closed | `nc -zv <VPS_IP> 2019` | Refused/timeout |
| 30 | Port 3000 closed | `nc -zv <VPS_IP> 3000` | Refused/timeout |
| 31 | Root SSH denied | `ssh root@<VPS_IP> -p 2222` | Permission denied |
| 32 | Password SSH denied | `ssh -o PubkeyAuthentication=no deploy@<VPS_IP> -p 2222` | Permission denied |
| 33 | VPS IP hidden | `dig +short A platform.yourdomain.dev` | NOT the VPS IP |

